---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ELRS Mobile - Control Your Hardware">
	<main>
		<header>
			<h1>ELRS <span class="text-gradient">Mobile</span></h1>
			<p class="tagline">Supports ELRS Versions 3.x.x and 4.x.x</p>
			<div class="cta-group">
				<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases" class="button primary">Download APK</a>
				<a href="/user_guide" class="button secondary">Documentation</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile" class="button secondary">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section id="overview">
			<h2>Overview</h2>
			<p>
				ELRS Mobile is a comprehensive open-source interface for managing ExpressLRS hardware. 
				Configure parameters, map PWM outputs, and flash firmware updates directly through your mobile device's WiFi or local network.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section id="demo">
			<h2>See it in Action</h2>
			<div class="video-container">
				<div class="phone-mockup">
					<iframe 
						width="100%" 
						height="100%" 
						src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6tukOoXa5aQ?autoplay=0&loop=1&rel=0&controls=1" 
						title="ELRS Mobile Demo" 
						frameborder="0" 
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
						allowfullscreen>
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="hardware">
			<h2>Supported Hardware</h2>
			<p>ELRS Mobile supports a wide range of ExpressLRS targets, focusing on Wi-Fi capable hardware.</p>
			<div class="hardware-grid">
				<div class="hw-card">
					<h4>Platforms</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>ESP8285</li>
						<li>ESP32</li>
						<li>ESP32-C3</li>
						<li>ESP32-S3</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="hw-card">
					<h4>Tested Targets</h4>
					<ul>
						<li>RadioMaster XR1 / XR4 Dual Band</li>
						<li>BETAFPV SuperP 14Ch (2.4G & 900M)</li>
						<li>HappyModel EP / EP Dual</li>
						<li>RadioMaster Nomad / Pocket</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="note">Currently unsupported: STM32 targets requiring serial STLink or Betaflight Passthrough.</p>
		</section>

		<section id="features" class="grid">
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Device Discovery</h3>
				<p>Seamlessly locate ELRS devices via mDNS, static AP IP (10.0.0.1), or manual override for complex networks.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Smart Flashing</h3>
				<p>The system patches firmware with your unique credentials (SSID, Binding Phrase) automatically before flashing OTA.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Connection Resilience</h3>
				<p>A multi-stage heartbeat monitor ensures you stay connected during transient network drops with a smart 30-second grace period.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h3>Expert Mode</h3>
				<p>Enable advanced auditing by saving assembled binaries locally for inspection or manual flashing via STLink/FTDI.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="installation">
			<h2>Installation</h2>
			<div class="install-steps">
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">1</span>
					<p>Go to <a href="https://github.com/wbhinton/ELRS-Mobile/releases">Releases</a> and download the latest <code>.apk</code>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">2</span>
					<p>Enable <strong>Install from Unknown Sources</strong> in your Android settings.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<span class="step-number">3</span>
					<p>Open the APK and follow the installation prompts.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer>
			<p>&copy; 2026 Weston Hinton. Distributed under the GNU GPL v3.</p>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	header {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary), #ffffff);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.tagline {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
	.cta-group {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	.button {
		padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
	}
	.button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	.button.primary {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
	}
	.button.secondary {
		border: 1px solid var(--primary);
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	section {
		padding: 3rem 0;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--surface);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.video-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}
	.phone-mockup {
		position: relative;
		width: 300px;
		height: 600px;
		background: #000;
		border: 12px solid #2d2d2d;
		border-radius: 36px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}
	.phone-mockup::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 150px;
		height: 25px;
		background: #2d2d2d;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 12px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;
		z-index: 10;
	}
	.hardware-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}
	.hw-card {
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}
	.hw-card h4 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--primary);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--background);
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.hw-card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
	.note {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	.card {
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}
	.card:hover {
		border-color: var(--primary);
	}
	.card h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--primary);
	}
	.install-steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	.step {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface);
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}
	.step-number {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-weight: bold;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 0;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface);
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}
	a {
		color: var(--primary);
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
